child.description:
&lt;p&gt;Resource number. Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Telephone Number&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Directory number block&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;PDP addresses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APNs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN owner&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The VPN the resource should belong to; used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;PDP addresses - mandatory&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APNs - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN owner - mandatory&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - mandatory&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Prefix of the VPN number. Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN owner - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Public number.Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - manadtory if REQUIRED_MAPPING_RULE is true&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Resource regulation of the public number.Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - manadtory if REQUIRED_MAPPING_RULE is true&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Service code.Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - manadtory if REQUIRED_MAPPING_RULE is true&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Indicator whether VPN private numbers should be searched according to the VPN mapping rule.
                                          Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If set to true, blocks of Directory numbers will be searched. Additionaly, limits can be specified.
                                          Can be used only in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Telephone number - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Minimum block size in case of searching for Block Directory Numbers. Only relevant if &lt;code&gt;SEARCH_BLOCK&lt;/code&gt;
                                          is set to true. Can be used only in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Telephone number - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maximum block size in case of searching for Block Directory Numbers. Only relevant if &lt;code&gt;SEARCH_BLOCK&lt;/code&gt;
                                          is set to true. Can be used only in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Telephone number - optional&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Flag indicating if resource reservation is enabled.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Reservation time is defined by Resource Settings: 'LockTime' in &lt;code&gt;Registry_CMS_Resource.xml&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;    Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Telephone Number&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Directory number block&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;PDP addresses&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APNs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN owner&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;In case if Content (instance Identifier) the resources are always reserved.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Customer identifier.Used in case of following Numbering Plan classes:
                                          &lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;VPN user - manadtory if REQUIRED_MAPPING_RULE is true&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
                                          &lt;/p&gt;
